'''Exmatriculation''' is the removal of a student's name from the list of current students when they leave a university.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.studium.uni-freiburg.de/studium-en/exmatrikulation-en/exmatrikulation-en?set_language=en|title=Exmatriculation — Studierendenportal|website=www.studium.uni-freiburg.de|language=en|access-date=2018-03-29}}</ref> It refers to the [[wikt:deregister|deregistering]] or [[wikt:unenroll|unenrolling]] of a student as a result of graduation, expulsion, inability to pay school fees, meet academic progress requirements or their self withdrawal from the university.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.ut.ee/en/exmatriculation|title=Exmatriculation|website=www.ut.ee|language=en|access-date=2018-03-29}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.fu-berlin.de/en/studium/studienorganisation/immatrikulation/exmatrikulation/index.html|title=Withdrawal from University (Exmatriculation)|date=2016-02-10|website=www.fu-berlin.de|language=en|access-date=2018-03-29}}</ref>

==After exmatriculation==
In cases of voluntary withdrawal, some schools, depending on their various conditions, may reimburse part of the fees if the student applies for it.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.uni-goettingen.de/en/refund+of+fees+already+paid/544363.html%20https://www.uni-osnabrueck.de/en/studies/exmatriculation.html%20https://www.uni-potsdam.de/en/studium/studying/organizing-your-studies/exmatriculation.html|title=Universität Göttingen - Georg-August-Universität Göttingen|last=Öffentlichkeitsarbeit|first=Georg-August-Universität Göttingen -|website=www.uni-goettingen.de|language=de|access-date=2018-03-29}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.uni-osnabrueck.de/en/studies/exmatriculation.html|title=Exmatriculation - Osnabrück University|website=www.uni-osnabrueck.de|language=en|access-date=2018-03-29}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.uni-potsdam.de/en/studium/studying/organizing-your-studies/exmatriculation.html|title=De-registration (Exmatrikulation) -  Organizing Your Studies -  Studying -  Studium - University of Potsdam|website=www.uni-potsdam.de|language=en|access-date=2018-03-29}}</ref> Unlike after a leave of absence, continuation of your studies following voluntary exmatriculation may be faced with difficulties.<ref name=":0">{{Cite web|url=https://www.uni-hohenheim.de/en/exmatriculation|title=Exmatriculation: University of Hohenheim|last=Hohenheim|first=University of|website=www.uni-hohenheim.de|language=en|access-date=2018-03-29}}</ref>

Expelled students are usually barred from being readmitted into the university where they got exmatriculated. However, in different cases, there are various exceptions and conditions for reapplying into the same university.<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.kaist.edu/html/en/edu/edu_03030303.html|title=Withdrawal/ Expulsion /Readmission|last=|first=|date=|website=|archive-url=|archive-date=|dead-url=|access-date=}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.hawkeyecollege.edu/students/handbook/suspended-expelled-students-readmission|title=Readmission After Suspension or Expulsion - Hawkeye Community College|website=www.hawkeyecollege.edu|language=en|access-date=2018-03-29}}</ref> There have also been cases of students whose expulsion was welcomed by the public's pressure and protests to revert it.<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.dvb.no/news/abfsu-nner-demand-re-admission-expelled-student-activist/75879|title=ABFSU, NNER demand re-admission of expelled student activist- DVB Multimedia Group|date=2017-06-05|work=DVB Multimedia Group|access-date=2018-03-29|language=en-US}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.nation.co.ke/news/1056-288138-lqbo40z/index.html|title=University to readmit expelled students|work=Daily Nation|access-date=2018-03-29|language=en-UK}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.the-star.co.ke/news/2017/12/05/three-uon-students-in-riot-case-readmitted-expulsion-quashed_c1679776|title=Three UoN students in riot case readmitted, expulsion quashed|work=The Star, Kenya|access-date=2018-03-29|language=en}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.premiumtimesng.com/regional/ssouth-west/252979-expelled-student-wins-case-nigerian-university.html|title=Expelled student wins case against Nigerian university - Premium Times Nigeria|date=2017-12-19|work=Premium Times Nigeria|access-date=2018-03-29|language=en-GB}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://sanfrancisco.cbslocal.com/2015/11/19/uc-berkeley-refuses-to-readmit-student-expelled-over-rape-allegations/amp/|title=UC Berkeley Refuses To Readmit Student Expelled Over Rape Allegations|date=2015-11-19|work=CBS San Francisco|access-date=2018-03-29|language=en-US}}</ref> Students who were exmatriculated due to failure to meet payment deadlines or continuous academic progress can also apply to be readmitted within a period of time depending on the school.<ref name=":0" />

