'''Geruma''' (also known as Gerema, Germa) is an [[Afro-Asiatic languages|Afro-Asiatic]] language spoken in [[Nigeria]].  Dialects include [[Duurum]] and [[Sum dialect|Sum]].  Speakers are shifting to [[Hausa language|Hausa]].<ref name=e18/>

