'''School supply stores''' sell teaching resources for parents, teachers and [[homeschooler]]s.  These stores frequently carry a wide selection of educational materials and decorations for classroom teachers such as books pencils pens and many other supplies.  A teacher store or [[learning store]] is often a member of the [[National School Supply and Equipment Association]].

